---
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader.astro';
---

<SectionHeader number="02" title="Experience" />

<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
  <details class="group rounded-lg bg-surface-dark p-6 shadow-sm" open="">
    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
          Lead Engineer <span class="text-primary">@ MONY Group</span>
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary">September 2019 - Present</p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="text-secondary transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">expand_more</span>
      </div>
    </summary>
    <div class="mt-4 text-secondary">
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2 pl-2">
        <li>
          Leading frontend engineering work across multiple projects, setting
          technical direction and ensuring high-quality delivery.
        </li>
        <li>
          Designing and building AI-powered chatbots, including multi-step
          agentic behaviour and tool-calling flows.
        </li>
        <li>
          Integrating generative UI systems using technologies like Vercel AI
          SDK, SkyBridge, and MCP-UI to produce adaptive, real-time UI
          components.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </details>
  <details class="group rounded-lg bg-surface-dark p-6 shadow-sm">
    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
          JavaScript Engineer <span class="text-primary">@ Barclays</span>
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary">
          January 2019 - August 2019
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="text-secondary transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">expand_more</span>
      </div>
    </summary>
    <div class="mt-4 text-secondary">
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2 pl-2">
        <li>
          Engineered and maintained major features of Scout's customer-facing
          web app using ES6, Handlebars, and Sass.
        </li>
        <li>
          Proposed and implemented scalable solutions to issues identified with
          cloud services and applications responsible for communicating with
          internal APIs.
        </li>
        <li>
          Interfaced with clients on a weekly basis, providing technological
          expertise and support.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </details>
  <details class="group rounded-lg bg-surface-dark p-6 shadow-sm">
    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
          Senior Frontend Engineer <span class="text-primary">@ JD Group</span>
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary">
          January 2017 - January 2019
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="text-secondary transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">expand_more</span>
      </div>
    </summary>
    <div class="mt-4 text-secondary">
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2 pl-2">
        <li>
          Engineered and maintained major features of Scout's customer-facing
          web app using ES6, Handlebars, and Sass.
        </li>
        <li>
          Proposed and implemented scalable solutions to issues identified with
          cloud services and applications responsible for communicating with
          internal APIs.
        </li>
        <li>
          Interfaced with clients on a weekly basis, providing technological
          expertise and support.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </details>
</div>
